{"tid":594671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國太平洋司令：習近平可能繼續掌權數十年　中國對美構成威脅","createTime":"2018-03-16T04:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:02.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bee682c4efe33f89fbcac387d5500831cf42653a","tid":594671,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"美國太平洋司令：習近平可能繼續掌權數十年　中國對美構成威脅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國全國人大會議通過修憲，刪除國家主席任期不得超過兩屆的規定，美國太平洋司令部司令哈里斯（Harry Harris）周四（15日）認為這可能令中國國家主席習近平，繼續掌權多數十年，他更指習近平在2049年中共建政一百年時，可能仍然擔任國家主席。他又指中國對美國構成重大威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈里斯周四出席參議院軍事委員會聽證會時，指中國利用了美國開放的態度，「我們過去希望把中國帶入世界貿易組織、讓中國參加我們的軍演等，以某種方式令中國像我們般，不過現實並不是如此，中國利用了美國的開放，仍然繼續自己一直在走的道路」。<br />\n<br />\n他批評中國正尋求地區霸權，希望踢走美國，而中國研發高超速音滑翔武器及隱型戰機，對美國構成重大威脅；他又關注中國將南海島礁軍事化，又對於中國即使無北冰洋邊界，但仍買入破冰船，表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n哈里斯亦有稱讚中國，落實聯合國安理會對朝鮮的制裁。不過若美國在對朝事宜上停滯不前，中國或會因而獲得戰略優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/168753/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%8C%E6%AC%8A%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F168753%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585&d=0rG8eEuMSB5i4WFv2BeHx3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=29e07c74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/168753/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%8C%E6%AC%8A%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85</a>"},{"pid":"786db4ba8b2e3f1a8ab751f52c7d9d303af9d8be","tid":594671,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba50b04db353cfab7bda50120af8648bc8ff9b02","tid":594671,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab53b844d1be64b604a668237ad32c316cc1b81","tid":594671,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"2049年&hellip;&hellip;98歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bda81f442848b7fab86a018de451ce148b39aff","tid":594671,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2049年&hellip;&hellip;98歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n96歲先啱"},{"pid":"4366f8f4d70f98d69dcb2132a32706977bc71101","tid":594671,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"大中華狗：畀時間大陸啦，大陸會變架<br />\n班大中華狗係咪落晒去陪屍屠華"}]}